    "language": "markdown",
    "value": "# Flappy UFO\r\nWe want to create a flappy bird clone with an UFO that has to avoid obstacles\r\n\r\n## Rules\r\n- UFO can move up and down\r\n- Obstacles move to the left\r\n- UFO falls down to the ground because of gravity\r\n- UFO goes up when pressing the mouse button\r\n- If UFO collides with obstacles or ground, the game is over\r\n\r\n## Order to build\r\n1. Draw the background\r\n2. Draw the UFO\r\n3. Add gravity to the UFO\r\n4. Make the UFO fly\r\n5. Detect collision between ground and UFO.\r\n6. ..."
  },
