    "value": ""
  },
  {
    "kind": 2,
    "language": "javascript",
    "value": "function setup() {\r\n  createCanvas(600, 300);\r\n  background(255, 255, 255);\r\n}"
  },
  {
    "kind": 1,
    "language": "markdown",
    "value": "#### Step 1\r\n\r\nDraw the background with a green ground..."
  },
  {
    "kind": 2,
    "language": "javascript",
    "value": "function scenery() {\r\n  push();\r\n  noStroke();\r\n  //draw the sky\r\n  fill(\"lightblue\");\r\n  rect(0, 0, width, height);\r\n\r\n  //draw the ground\r\n  fill(\"green\");\r\n  rect(0, 200, width, height);\r\n  pop();\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction draw() {\r\n  scenery();\r\n}"
  },
  {
    "kind": 1,
    "language": "markdown",
    "value": "#### Step 2\r\nDraw the UFO, don't forget to add x and y as a parameter, because the UFO needs to move"
  },
  {
    "kind": 2,
    "language": "javascript",
    "value": "function ufo(x, y) {\r\n  push();\r\n  translate(x, y);\r\n\r\n  //saucer\r\n  fill(255, 0, 0);\r\n  ellipse(0, 0, 80, 30);\r\n\r\n  //Glass dome\r\n  fill(255, 255, 255, 100);\r\n  beginShape();\r\n  vertex(-20, 0);\r\n  bezierVertex(-20, 5, 20, 5, 20, 0);\r\n  bezierVertex(20, -40, -20, -40, -20, 0);\r\n  endShape();\r\n  pop();\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction draw() {\r\n  scenery();\r\n  ufo(100, 100);\r\n}"
  },
  {
    "kind": 1,
    "language": "markdown",
    "value": "#### Step 3\r\nAdd gravity to the UFO by using a variable for the y-position of the UFO and add velocity and acceleration"
  },
  {
    "kind": 2,
    "language": "javascript",
    "value": "let ufoY = 100;\r\nlet velocity = 1;\r\nlet acceleration = 0.1;\r\n\r\nfunction draw() {\r\n  scenery();\r\n  ufo(100, ufoY);\r\n\r\n  ufoY += velocity;\r\n  velocity += acceleration;\r\n}"
  },
